2017-05-05  Lukas Kluft  <lukas.kluft@gmail.com>

	* typhon/plots/plots.py:

	* (channels): Fixed handling of second offset.

	Now correctly used around the position of the first passband.

	* (HectoPascalFormatter): Simplified implementation.

	Replaced the `partial` solution with an explicit function.
	This also allows a proper docstring.

	* (profile_p): Fixed docstring description (report by Oliver).

