	* doc/conf.py:

	Include sphinx.ext.intersphinx to reference Python, SciPy and matplotlib
	documentation.

	Set a default plot preamble. Currently only seeding numpy's random number
	generator to make plots in documentation not so random ;)

	* doc/pyplots/plot_qualitative2.py: Remove np.random.seed().

	* typhon/plots/cm/_cm.py:

	Adjust the bright yellow in qualitative1 to the one used in qualitative2.

	* typhon/plots/plots.py:

	Fixed heatmap() documentation. Also included a small example.

